Domestic violence sickens me. Which is why I called 911 when I saw a man beating his wife tonight while walking home with Kevin. So we come up on this corner, and I hear a loud crack (which was the guy's kid throwing the door open, I think) so I look over, and I see this man bearing down on his wife... All I can remember is the kids screaming, and the wife yelling... I never want to hear that again. Ever, ever, ever. And I gave my info to the police. I'll be glad to serve as a witness at any trial to put the son of a bitch in jail. So we called 911. And we waited. And the fucker came out of his house. And his neighbor asked him, "is your daughter OK?" "Oh, she's just fucking around again." And it took every ounce of restraint I had to not shout obscenities at him. Justice shall be served with not an iron fist, but a gavel of gold.

I'm so so so so so so so so so so tired of this place. I'm so so so so so so so so so so tired of this feeling. I'm so so so so so so so so so so tired of everybody. I'm getting sick. Sick of people sick of facades and not saying what we really feel and sick of talking like nobody hears a word I fucking say so you can all just go fuck an animal for all I care. Guess what, I don't care what you want anymore. I don't have time to give a shit about you. I don't have the shit left to give, you're full of it already, why should I give more? I want the whole world to disappear. I've been severely discouraged. I can't even think about functioning like a normal human being, let alone what I'm supposed to be. You're all so goddamn depressing. And those of you I actually enjoy can't seem to spare me five minutes over the rest of the world, so whatever. You're so fixated on allllllll the things that just DON'TDON'TDON'TDON'TMATTTTTTERRRRRRRRRR. Pull your head out of your ass, eh? Save us the bitching about how all you see is bullshit. lksfjdfkdfsdfjkdf You say you want money, girls, friends, answers, well you can start by going ahead and fucking yourself because it'll get you closer than any of your BITCHING will. You call me a whiny little bitch when you can't seem to shut your own mouth? I have my own problems, I don't need YOU fuckers adding to it by calling me a FAKEFRAUDWHATEVER. If you need something to make you feel better about yourself, then don't use putting me down as a solution. Last I checked we were still human, though I can't seem to tell the difference between the rest of the world and slimy fucking roaches. Well, guess what? I'm sick of having a heart and feeling and all sorts of otherlkjerlkajsf;lkajsdf;lk BULLSHIT. Do you know that if RIGHT THIS MOMENT I were to hear one of you died I wouldn't feel a SHRED of remorse for a good ten minutes? I really forgot to care that you hate me this time. Guess what? In two years I'll be out of this steaming shitpile for the rest of my fucking life while you all rot in your own piss. I'll be laughing when your 'friends' you so casually regard so much higher than me won't show enough care to bury your ass in the shit you stand on when you die. And I'll be laughing when it turns out a pretty face won't get you much more than an STD from the girl who was too cute to ever look at me. Go fuck yourselves, world. I hope you all die soon and painfully, every last one of you ungrateful heartless assfucks. :]

So aside from feeling sick the past couple of days and being bored shitless this week has been good so far. :]

ARGH

This cold is stronger than a French hooker's stench.

Mmm. Fresh air.

I think the rain pulled out every little bit of pollution from the valley.

Tastes like it. :]

) You are walking through a forest. What does it look like?
Pine trees. It's cold. There's snow on the ground. Not a living thing for miles. Empty. Alone, but beautiful in its own sense.

2) You walk through the forest until you find a body of water. What does it look like?
A relatively small brook. The water is cold and flows fast. Small, smooth stones litter the bottom.

3) You keep walking and find a jar. What does it look like?
Chipped at the top. The lid is missing. It's a little dirty.

4) You run into a bear. What do you do?
Play dead, or find my way back before it notices me.

5) You find a key. What does it look like?
Old. Rusted in places. A dark gold color.

6) You find a stone. What's it look like?
Smooth, shining. Frosted over. Strange colors cover it.

7) You leave the forest. What do you see beyond it?
Mountains. Empty, cold mountains.

8) What do you think of when you hear the word destruction?
Man.


Meanings: 

1) The forest represents your life.
Relatively accurate.

2) The body of water represents your sex/love life.
I wish.

3) The jar is your marriage.
...

4) The incident with the bear is how you deal with problems.
I don't know about that...

5) The key is your knowlege.
...

6) The stone is your heart.
...

7) What you see past the forest is your future life.
Hm.

8) The image from the word destruction is your demise.
That much I can believe.
God, I can't wait for this all to just end.

I am in a hole. I am a worm digging my way through a nice big steaming pile of shit. I must be the worst person to ever live, and hell if I even know why. I'm looking up at the soles of everbody else's shoes and I am downright amazed. I feel so small, so weak, so pitiful. I am the most disgusting, contorted, horrible waste of space to ever walk the earth. I'm disgusting. Low. Pitiful. A walking, miserable waste of space. I'm sick. I'm wrong. I'm horrible. And I'm too fucking stupid to even be able to pull myself up out of this fucking hole. I don't even blame the people that treat me like shit anymore. I am shit. I always have been shit, and I am always going to be shit. I'm not even worthless. I'm in the fucking negatives. I'd kill just to be worthless. I can't do a thing for myself or for anybody else. I am a little bit of nothing in the face of everything.

You scored as Christianity. Your views are most similar to those of Christianity. Do more research on Christianity and possibly consider being baptized and accepting Jesus, if you aren't already Christian. Christianity is the second of the Abrahamic faiths; it follows Judaism and is followed by Islam. It differs in its belief of Jesus, as not a prophet nor historical figure, but as God in human form. The Holy Trinity is the concept that God takes three forms: the Father, the Son (Jesus), and the Holy Ghost (sometimes called Holy Spirit). Jesus taught the idea of instead of seeking revenge, one should love his or her neighbors and enemies. Christians believe that Jesus died on the cross to save humankind and forgive people's sins.

I feel like the most disgusting creature to walk the face of the earth. And I really don't care if you "totally disagree" or "really think I'm being too hard on myself", because I'm really sick of people contradicting me every time I try to explain myself. I spend so, so, so much time lying on the ground, it's sad. I spent another hour or so lying in the park. My bike shit out on me halfway home. So yeah. Eat sleep grass. And maybe get a little in my skin, too. I realized that, hey- That's going to be what death is like. A few seconds of, "Oh, shit. Well, I guess it's over?" Then...gone? I don't make sense anymore. I need sleep. School blows. Hooray for breaking things. Joe, I'm going to steal your trademark once more...wait for it... The end.

You like things edgy, subtle, and smart. I guess that means you're probably an intellectual, but don't take that to mean pretentious. You realize 'dumb' can be witty--after all isn't that the Simpsons' philosophy?--but rudeness for its own sake, 'gross-out' humor and most other things found in a fraternity leave you totally flat.

I guess you just have a more cerebral approach than most. You have the perfect mindset for a joke writer or staff writer.

Your sense of humor takes the most thought to appreciate, but it's also the best, in my opinion.

You probably loved the Office. If you don't know what I'm talking about, check it out here: http://www.bbc.co.uk/comedy/theoffice/.
